<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 09:09:57 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a589fcfd4785</link><description>&lt;p&gt;卢浮宫-朗斯&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Louvre-Lens" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/6a589fcfd4785.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 09:09:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>雨夜独享台球时光</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5892ed95cc6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;昨晚我们顺道去了Society Garden，那是家靠近我们家的舒适户外啤酒花园酒吧。因为下雨，人流稀少，所以我们在游戏室打了几小时台球。平时这里拥挤很多，能几乎独享整个地方感觉真好。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A quiet outdoor bar at twilight, with colorful string lights and warm Edison bulbs glowing above the serving counters. The nearly empty beer garden has a relaxed, inviting atmosphere, with trees silhouetted against the deep blue evening sky." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a5892ed95cc6.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 08:14:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a587324e63e9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;继续练习HTML/CSS，这次制作一个带右侧边栏的布局。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bare-bones webpage with a header, main content area, sidebar with an author bio, and a footer" height="1688" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a587324e63e9.png" width="2552"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:59:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>单列页面布局练习</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5872d2a3e7a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;HTML和CSS练习：制作一列页面布局&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Plain HTML page displaying placeholder text in a one-column layout" height="1430" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a5872d2a3e7a.png" width="1542"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:57:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a57def86f2c7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;抱歉，我们已经打烊了。营业中，请进。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="White storefront on a street corner with white iron bars on all of the windows and the front door. Everything is weathered. There is one sign in the window that reads “sorry, we’re closed,” and a second in an adjacent window that reads “open, come in.” There are wig busts in the window with various head wraps on them. A sign painted on the concrete at the entryway reads “national shirt shops coast to coast.”" height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/6a57def86f2c7.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:26:51 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>